Serializable
public class SubtreeAnalyzerByRule
extends SubtreeAnalyzer

Perform a subtree analysis using a rule criterion. Currently this only counts subtrees, and returns the k most common subtrees using at most r rule expansions (AnalyzeSubtrees).
